# ✅ Problem 2: Secure Game Save System

### ✔️ Clean Code

```java
import java.io.*;

class PlayerProfile implements Serializable {
    private String username;
    private int score;
    private transient String password;

    public PlayerProfile(String username, int score, String password) {
        this.username = username;
        this.score = score;
        this.password = password;
    }

    @Override
    public String toString() {
        return "User: " + username + ", Score: " + score + ", Password: " + password;
    }
}

class GameSaveManager {
    public void saveProfile(PlayerProfile profile) {
        try {
            ObjectOutputStream out = new ObjectOutputStream(new FileOutputStream("save.dat"));
            out.writeObject(profile);
            out.close();
            System.out.println("Game saved (password not included).");
        } catch (IOException e) {
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
```

### 🔍 Key Idea

* `Serializable` → object file এ save করা যাবে
* `transient` → sensitive data (password) save হবে না

👉 Short line:
**Security = transient keyword**

