# ✅ Problem 4: Abstract & Access Control

### ✔️ Clean Code

```java
abstract class MediaDevice {

    protected void pairHardware() {
        System.out.println("Hardware paired successfully.");
    }

    public abstract void playAudio();
}

class SmartSpeaker extends MediaDevice {

    @Override
    public void playAudio() {
        pairHardware();
        System.out.println("Playing audio...");
    }
}

class AppController {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        SmartSpeaker speaker = new SmartSpeaker();
        speaker.playAudio();

        // speaker.pairHardware(); ❌ error (protected)
    }
}
```

### 🔍 Key Idea

* `abstract` → object বানানো যাবে না
* `protected` → শুধু subclass access করতে পারবে

👉 Short line:
**Access control = protected + abstract**

